title: Korean Royal Court Stir Fried Rice Cakes (Gungjung-tteokbokki: 궁중떡볶이)
description:
The recipe is here! https://www.maangchi.com/recipe/gungjung-tteokbokki
Gungjung-ddeokbokki is actually the original ddeokbokki and is very different than the more well-known red, spicy version. This was before hot peppers were introduced or popular in Korea, so it isn't spicy at all.
